; Regression test for issue #949: convert csv to journal and save it to .dat (BZ#949)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/949
;
; The issue requested the ability to convert a CSV file to ledger journal format.
; The `convert` command fulfills this: it reads a CSV file and generates journal entries
; that can be saved to a .dat file (e.g., via shell redirection or --output flag).

test -f /dev/null convert $sourcepath/test/input/convert-test.csv --input-date-format %Y/%m/%d -> 0
2024/01/15 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Unknown                             -50
    Equity:Unknown

2024/01/20 * Gas Station
    Expenses:Unknown                             -30
    Equity:Unknown
end test
